{"tid":159586,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"旺角騷亂3被告判囚3年　代表律師均稱會上訴","createTime":"2017-03-17T06:08:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-18T21:02:53.000Z","uid":48093,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"92389c02ec2de761a28ccef0523863ccdf5500a0","tid":159586,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T06:08:34.000Z","msg":"旺角騷亂案中三名被告，被裁定暴動罪罪名成立，各被判入獄三年。三人的代表律師均表示，會提出上訴。<br />\n<br />\n首被告許嘉琪的代表律師表示，應該會就定罪及刑期提出上訴，保釋未有決定，上訴原因要再作研究。<br />\n<br />\n第二被告麥子晞的代表律師表示，會就定罪及刑期提出上訴，未決定會否申請保釋，未來希望跟另外兩位律師討論就上訴有一致的決定，及往後如何辯解。<br />\n<br />\n第三被告薛達榮的代表律師表示，考慮上訴。他又透露，薛達榮聞判時表現平靜，他亦有心理準備收監，他們會研究判詞再作決定，對判刑不評論。"},{"pid":"5fce1aacf8dd979388368100bdc2a217275dcc0c","tid":159586,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T06:09:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d954e13cac02584b5acb8baf794a30f4b7266d56","tid":159586,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T17:12:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04e15c87b3eabfcb0242d5014161534ab0c77446","tid":159586,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T02:42:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9e489bbe9d88131f6593d482cdafa9ea43a4413","tid":159586,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T14:46:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d34b6e754a418ceac9034fb26070780fa37f9cd2","tid":159586,"uid":60404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T14:48:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2b663be8348a379c045881ecd79dde7b59c664d","tid":159586,"uid":2649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T14:51:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\"